pullRequest.body:
This merges the two files `Analysis/Complex/Convex.lean` and `Analysis/Convex/Complex.lean`, putting lemmas about convexity in the complex plane together; and moves a lemma from `UpperHalfPlane/Topology.lean` to this file, substantially shortening the import path to all the C-star-algebras files.

---
